OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely cloudy morning,
OL,6,Fhowever some brighter spells possible
OL,7,Fin the east at first. Outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain and drizzle pushing across the
OL,9,Fregion during the day. Strengthening
OL,10,Fwinds and near normal temperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOften cloudy with further
OL,13,Foutbreaks of patchy drizzle at first.
OL,14,FStrengthening winds will herald a band
OL,15,Fof heavier rain later in the night.
OL,16,FGusty winds particularly near Bristol
OL,17,FChannel coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
