OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FRain soon clearing to the
OL,6,Feast tomorrow with sunny spells and
OL,7,Fshowers following. These locally heavy
OL,8,Fwith hail and a risk of thunder.
OL,9,FRather breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,12,FUnsettled on Sunday with a mixture of
OL,13,Fsunny spells and showers. Often cloudy
OL,14,FMonday and Tuesday, with few showers
OL,15,Fin the mix. Temperatures generally
OL,16,Fclose to average. Windy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
